# Manchester City
![logo](data:image/png;base64,)


[*Manchester City*](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Manchester_City_F.C.) is a English football club that competes in the best leagues in the world with the [*Premier League*](https://www.premierleague.com/) and [*Champions League*](https://www.uefa.com/uefachampionsleague/).

## About
Manchester City recently has won many Premier League titles, 4 in the last 5 years to be exact.
With many talanted world class players like Kevin De Bruyne, Phil Foden, and Erling Haaland, this football
club is seen to be one of the best teams in football history under one of the top managers, Pep Guardiola.

## Goals
This football club has won many trophies over the years but have yet to win arguably the most important trophy there is.
With many recent signings this year, the team is projected to win the most prestegious trophy in the world, the Champions League.
### Erling Haaland

The signing of Haaland was one of the biggest signings of the summer, with Manchester City desperately needing
a striker, Haaland is seen to be the last piece of the puzzle for City, with hopes to finally win the teams first UCL.

###Kevin De Bruyne

De Bruyne was signed to City in 2015, in which he has already broke the record for most club assists. 
He is seen to be as one of the best midfielders in the world, making the pairing of De Bruyne and Haaland
one of the best duos in football history.

## What's next?
Manchester City began to take over the Premier League and now have their eyes set on the Champions League.
